{"id": 231325114, "title": "Whitehead man on ladder video leads to 'firearm' arrest", "text": "A 66-year-old male has been arrested after a video circulated online showing a man on a ladder brandishing what appears to be a gun. The video shows the man climb the ladder towards a Northern Ireland flag, however he stops short of the banner. During a brief exchange with the man filming the incident the man on the ladder reaches for a black 'pistol' and holds it aloft. It is unclear if the suspected firearm is real or imitation. Read more: Drugs worth estimated \u00a3600k seized in \u201csophisticated cannabis factory\u201d raid Read more: Man found with \u201csignificant head injury\u201d leads to attempted murder arrest In a statement issued on Saturday afternoon, the PSNI said detectives in Antrim \u201care aware of a video circulating online in the Whitehead area on Friday evening, 7th June\u201d. A police spokesman added: \u201cAn investigation has been launched into the content of the video and follow up searches have been conducted today, Saturday 8th June, in the area. \u201cA 66-year-old man has subsequently been arrested on suspicion of possession of a firearm or imitation firearm with the intent to cause fear of violence. \u201cHe remains in custody at this time as enquiries continue. We would urge anyone with information to call us on 101 quoting reference number 1914 07/06/24. Alternatively, you can submit a report online using the non-emergency reporting form via www.psni.police.uk/makeareport/.\u201d For all the latest news, visit the Belfast Live homepage here and sign up to our daily newsletter here.", "summary": "&quot;66-year-old man has subsequently been arrested on suspicion of possession of a firearm or imitation firearm with the intent to cause fear of violence&quot;", "url": "https://www.belfastlive.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/whitehead-man-ladder-video-leads-29318873", "image": "https://i2-prod.belfastlive.co.uk/news/northern-ireland/article29319099.ece/ALTERNATES/s1200/0_unnamed-1-1.png", "video": null, "publish_date": "2024-06-08 15:59:20", "author": "Maurice Fitzmaurice", "authors": ["Maurice Fitzmaurice"], "language": "en", "source_country": "gb", "sentiment": -0.042}